THE ROLE
Expand all
Our client is on the search for a candidate who will:
• Have basic accounting knowledge
•2-5 years of work experience within the accounting field
• Experience within a retail / luxury brand would be preferred.
The successful candidate should possess:
• Minimum Bachelors degree in Accounting.
•Experience in processing payment vouchers, accounting documents, verifying purchase orders and reconciliation of vendor accounts.
• Fluent in English.
